533
00:31:18,770 --> 00:31:23,350
ALIEN 1: Good luck, J!
ALIEN 2: This planet's toast. Ha-ha-ha.

534
00:31:25,080 --> 00:31:27,220
♫

535
00:31:39,260 --> 00:31:41,640
