572
00:33:08,310 --> 00:33:09,990
Very rare, very old.

573
00:33:10,150 --> 00:33:12,320
But first, we gotta get high.

574
00:33:12,550 --> 00:33:13,860
Hey. No.

575
00:33:14,250 --> 00:33:16,700
